name: Tau's Anya [Legacy]
description:
Anya Geraldine's LoRa


She is indonesian actress. Im sharing my own trained lora, since there are already multiple version of her in civitai. Use at your own discretion and i do not support sharing indecent generation of her.

IS NOT A MINOR (21+)

DO NOT USE THIS FOR COMMERCIAL PURPOSE

Works best with henmix model.

henmix_real - v2.3_pruned | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai


Trigger word is = anyager (if needed)

Lora Weight = 0.1-0.9 ( 0.4 / 0.6 / 0.8 is best )

For best result use Dynamic CFG Threshold:

  • Mimic = 10

  • Min. Mimic Scale = 0, Cosine Up

  • CFG Scale Sch. = 15, Half Cosine Down

If subject face is small / far away use: DDetailer Script with bbox anime face with default settings except denoiser at 0.2-0.3. You can combine this LoRa with a lot of other Style / Attire / Pose / Acts LoRa, Also works well with character LyCoris.

Please leave a review if you have any critiques or if you find this LoRa good.
